ass=\"inner\" style=\"background-image:url(https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index1-2.jpg)\"></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n       <div class=\"inner\" style=\"background-image:url(https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index1-5.jpg)\"></div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"txtWrap\">\n     <div class=\"inner\">\n      \t     <section class=\"no-results not-found\">\n\t<header class=\"page-header\">\n\t\t<h1 class=\"page-title\">何も見つかりませんでした</h1>\n\t</header>\n\t<div class=\"page-content\">\n\t\t<p>このカテゴリーの求人は現在ございません。<br>カテゴリーを変更すればあなたにぴったりの求人があるかもしれません。<br>検索条件を変えて再度お探しください。</p>\n\t</div><!-- .page-content -->\n</section><!-- .no-results -->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"secIndex sec2\">\n   \t<div class=\"innerWrap\">\n \t <div class=\"inner inview\">\n  \t  <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index2-3.png\" alt=\"\">\n  \t  <p class=\"ceoText\">\n  \t   <span class=\"animated\"><b class=\"emphasis\">従業員が最高に働きやすい環境が</b></span>\n  \t   <span class=\"animated\"><b class=\"emphasis\">最高の企業だと思う。</b></span>\n  \t  </p>\n   \t  <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/about/vision#sec1\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">代表メッセージ</p></a>\n \t </div>\n \t <div class=\"loopWrap\">\n \t  <div class=\"loopTable\">\n \t   <div class=\"loopCenter\">\n \t    <div class=\"loopSlider\">\n \t     <ul>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/au1-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/cul1-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index2-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/cul1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t      <li><img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n \t     </ul>\n \t    </div>\n \t   </div>\n \t  </div>\n \t </div>\n   \t</div>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"secIndex sec3\">\n   \t<div class=\"innerWrap\">\n   \t <div class=\"flexWrap\">\n   \t  <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n   \t   <div class=\"inner\">\n   \t    <h2>\n   \t     <span class=\"en\">ABOUT US</span>\n   \t     <span class=\"jp\">ミライトリンクについて</span>\n   \t    </h2>\n   \t    <p class=\"txt\">1984年に奈良市四条大路にて『寿司・割烹 甚八本店』を創業して以来30余年。形を変えながら今日まで歩んで参りました。今では奈良県を中心とした近隣府県に7拠点を構え、今でも拡大を続ける仕出し・割烹のベンチャー企業です。</p>\n   \t    <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/about/company\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">会社概要</p></a>\n   \t   </div>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t  <div class=\"flexRight\">\n   \t   <div class=\"inner\">\n        <div class=\"aspect aspect50\">\n         <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n  \t      <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n         </div>\n        </div>\n   \t   </div>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t </div>\n   \t</div>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"secIndex sec4\">\n   \t<div class=\"innerWrap\">\n   \t <div class=\"flexWrap\">\n   \t  <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n   \t   <h2>\n   \t    <span class=\"en\">INTERVIEW</span>\n   \t    <span class=\"jp\">先輩インタビュー</span>\n   \t   </h2>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t  <div class=\"flexRight\">\n   \t   <p class=\"txt\">無数にある企業から弊社 株式会社ミライトリンクを選び、一緒になって働いている各社員に話を聞きました。会社について・仕事について・やりがいについて。</p>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t  <div class=\"flexCenter\">\n   \t  \n   \t   <div class=\"swiper-container\">\n   \t    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n   \t    \n        \t         \n         <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n          <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/c-iv/staff-2\" class=\"linkFull\"></a>\n          <div class=\"flexInner\">\n           <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n            <div class=\"aspect aspect141\">\n             <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n              <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/iv1-2.png\" alt=\"\">\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flexRight\">\n            <dl class=\"listProfile\">\n             <dd><p>2011年度入社</p></dd>\n             <dt><p>伊藤 秀紀</p></dt>\n             <dd><p>甚八運営本部</p></dd>\n             <dd><p>統括マネージャー</p></dd>\n            </dl>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n    \n            \n         <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n          <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/c-iv/staff-4\" class=\"linkFull\"></a>\n          <div class=\"flexInner\">\n           <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n            <div class=\"aspect aspect141\">\n             <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n              <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/iv1-5.png\" alt=\"\">\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flexRight\">\n            <dl class=\"listProfile\">\n             <dd><p>2014年度入社</p></dd>\n             <dt><p>市川 竹大</p></dt>\n             <dd><p>甚八 香芝店</p></dd>\n             <dd><p>料理長</p></dd>\n            </dl>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n    \n            \n         <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n          <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/c-iv/staff-5\" class=\"linkFull\"></a>\n          <div class=\"flexInner\">\n           <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n            <div class=\"aspect aspect141\">\n             <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n              <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/iv1-4.png\" alt=\"\">\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flexRight\">\n            <dl class=\"listProfile\">\n             <dd><p>2001年度入社</p></dd>\n             <dt><p>絈井 敦史</p></dt>\n             <dd><p>甚八 橿原店</p></dd>\n             <dd><p>店長兼料理長</p></dd>\n            </dl>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n    \n            \n         <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n          <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/c-iv/staff-6\" class=\"linkFull\"></a>\n          <div class=\"flexInner\">\n           <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n            <div class=\"aspect aspect141\">\n             <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n              <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/iv1-7.png\" alt=\"\">\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flexRight\">\n            <dl class=\"listProfile\">\n             <dd><p>2015年度入社</p></dd>\n             <dt><p>濱本 昭伸</p></dt>\n             <dd><p>甚八運営本部</p></dd>\n             <dd><p>食部門 総料理長</p></dd>\n            </dl>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n    \n            \n         <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n          <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/c-iv/staff-9\" class=\"linkFull\"></a>\n          <div class=\"flexInner\">\n           <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n            <div class=\"aspect aspect141\">\n             <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n              <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/iv1-10.png\" alt=\"\">\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flexRight\">\n            <dl class=\"listProfile\">\n             <dd><p>2017年度入社</p></dd>\n             <dt><p>岡田 隆正</p></dt>\n             <dd><p>甚八 四条大路店</p></dd>\n             <dd><p>寿司場 調理</p></dd>\n            </dl>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n    \n           \t    \n        </div>\n       </div>\n       \n       <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/interview\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">先輩インタビュー</p></a>\n   \t  \t\n   \t  </div>\n   \t </div>\n   \t</div>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"secIndex sec5\">\n   \t<div class=\"innerWrap\">\n   \t <div class=\"flexWrap\">\n   \t  <div class=\"flexLeft\">\n   \t   <div class=\"inner\">\n   \t    <h2>\n   \t     <span class=\"en\">WELFARE</span>\n   \t     <span class=\"jp\">制度・環境</span>\n   \t    </h2>\n   \t    <p class=\"txt\">『全従業員とその家族の物心両面の幸福を追求する』これが弊社 株式会社甚八が掲げる大切な使命です。美味しい料理を通してお客様を笑顔にするのはもちろんのこと、その作り手たちにも笑顔が生まれ、安心して毎日を過ごせるように。常に会社が前進し続ける原動力として３つのポリシーと10個の約束を掲げていています。</p>\n   \t    <div class=\"btnWrap\">\n         <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/culture/flow\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">業務の流れ</p></a>\n         <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/culture/enviroment\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">働く環境</p></a>\n         <a href=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/culture/welfare\" class=\"btn md\"><p class=\"txt\">福利厚生・教育制度</p></a>\n   \t    </div>\n   \t   </div>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t  <div class=\"flexRight\">\n   \t   <div class=\"inner\">\n   \t    <div class=\"aspect aspect100\">\n   \t     <div class=\"aspectBlock\">\n   \t      <figure class=\"fig1\">\n   \t       <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/index5-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n   \t      </figure>\n   \t      <figure class=\"fig2\">\n   \t       <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/cul1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n   \t      </figure>\n   \t      <figure class=\"fig3\">\n   \t       <img src=\"https://miraitolink.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/zinpachi/images/cul1-3.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n   \t      </figure>\n   \t     </div>\n   \t    </div>\n   \t   </div>\n   \t  </div>\n   \t </div>\n   \t</div>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"secIndex sec6\">\n   \t<div class=\"innerWrap first\">\n   \t <h2>\n   \t  <span class=\"en\">RECRUITMENT</span>\n   \t  <span class=\"jp\">採用情報</span>\n   \t </h2>\n   \t <p class=\"txt\">現在募集中の採用情報をご案内します。</p>\n   \t <ul class=\"listIndex6\">\n   \t  <li>\n   \t   <dl class=\"list